photos.description:
Love is Not Love
4/6 Will has completed his final sonnet and senses literary immortality just around the corner

The Quality of Mercy
6/6 When Will's savings go missing, he is forced to make an unusual bargain with his rival.

What Bloody Man is That?
5/6 The plague leads Will and his friends to escape to the family home in Stratford.

The Apparel Proclaims The Man
3/6 Will hopes to move up in the world when he is invited to Lord Southampton's party.

The Play's the Thing
2/6 Will's controversial new play is about to be presented to the queen when it goes missing.

Star Crossed Lovers
1/6 Will struggles to find inspiration for Romeo and has to deal with an angry actor.
